# Origin of the melon-server JSON API. middleware.ts proxies /v1/* and /healthz
# here at request time, so the browser only ever talks to this front-end's own
# origin and the session cookie flows unchanged. Read at RUNTIME, so the same
# build works against any environment.
#
# Copy to .env.local for local development.
MELON_API_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8080
